name: Thieves on FIAT500
description:
This work was made to commemorate the achievement of 500 followers.
‘If they team up, they can steal anything. Even if it's a car running on a rainbow. ‘
This work is a collaboration work with Ninacrypto and CRYPTONINJAS , and the motif is Lupine III and his friends on the FIAT500.  I would like to express my sincere gratitude to the two for accepting the collaboration offer.
